Take 6 ounces of hot Italian sausage and form 3 (2-ounce) slider patties. Grill the hot Italian sausage patties on grill or griddle for 6-7 min. Before finished, top with mozzarella cheese. Toast the sesame rolls and assemble by placing a grilled cheesed patty, sliced tomato, and fresh basil on the sesame roll bottom. Top with basil aioli and sesame roll top. Serve with potato wedges tossed in parmesan cheese.